imdb.plot outline: "Immortal Songs: Singing the Legend" is a South Korean singing competition program. Hosted by Shin Dong Yup, each show features seven contemporary singers who perform their reinterpreted versions of songs by the same legendary singer. The order of the performances is determined by a random drawing, and the 500-member audience votes for their favorite performance of the night.
